categories: Category:Songs by The Emperor's New Clothes

nodes.text: "Section 223" was a song by the pro-Imperial minga musical group The Emperor's New Clothes from their album Artistic Integrity, which was considered the band's newest release at some point during the period of time between 0 ABY and 4 ABY. Like the rest of The Emperor's New Clothes' work, "Section 223" was approved by the Imperial Board of Culture.

"Section 223" was one of the songs by The Emperor's New Clothes listed in Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim, a 1993 supplement to West End Games' Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game written by Simon Smith and Eric S. Trautmann.
